window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>A troubled past, a magical future, and a new adventure!</i></b></p> <p>After the adventures to secure the gates of hell, Argo finds himself bouncing from contract to contract. A mercenary wizard's life is never dull and it turns fascinating when he arrives in Sekretto. Join Argo and Rekkles as they're hired to investigate an escalation in the region's volcanic activity. The contract to escort the survey teams is especially interesting because it just may be Argo's last.</p>"; 
